<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Heinrich XVI. von Wittelsbach, Herzog von Bayern-Landshut</head><p>Der Rat bittet erneut um Herausgabe von vier ganzen und vier halben in einer Herberge zu Landshut beschlagnahmten Tuchen des Christian Woltzhofer, Bürger zu Nürnberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_138" id="68v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_138_r2l1">Hercʒog <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_138_r2l2">Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / 
<del rend="strikethrough">vns hat fürgelegt </del> Als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> vormals </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l3"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von Criſtan wolcʒhofens <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> wegen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l4">vvie man Jm cʒu landſhute in des vrban fünfingers 
<del rend="strikethrough">hawſe </del> <expan>herb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l5">aufgehalten hab vier gancʒe / vnd vier halbe tuche in <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> groen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l6">v̈mbſlag / vnd daʒ er <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tuche vor vns ʒu den <expan>heılıg<ex>en</ex></expan> behabt hab </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l7">daʒ die ſein vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> ſein Alſo daʒ khein auſʒman vveder </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l8">teil noch gemein daran hab / Nu iſt derſelb <expan>unſ<ex>er</ex></expan> burger <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l9">für vns kumen / vnd hat vns furgelegt / vvie Jm <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſeine tuche </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l10">noch niht vvidervvorden ſeẏn / <expan>Dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr noch durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l11">vvilligen dinſte <expan>vvılle<ex>n</ex></expan> von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> ſchicken vnd <expan>beſtelle<ex>n</ex></expan> vvöllet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l12">daʒ dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> burger <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſeine tuche wider vverden / Als etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l13">das wöllen etc / vnd biten des <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnedige <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> vvider </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l14"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>r</ex>ıa</expan> vj <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Joh<ex>annis</ex></expan> <expan>Bap<ex>tis</ex><hi rend="sup">te</hi></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_138" id="68v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Herczog <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> vormals
              <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von Cristan Wolczhofens, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, wegen, wie man im czu Landshute in des Urban Fünfingers
                <expan>herb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> aufgehalten hab vier gancze und vier halbe tuche in
                <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> groen ümbslag und daz er
              <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tuche vor uns zu den
              <expan>heilig<ex>en</ex></expan> behabt hab, daz die sein und
              <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> sein, also daz khein auszman weder teil noch gemein daran
            hab, nu ist derselb <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burger
              <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> für uns kumen und hat uns furgelegt, wie im
                <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> seine tuche noch niht widerworden seyn.
                <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir noch durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
            willigen dinste <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> schicken und <expan>bestelle<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet,
            daz dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> burger <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> seine tuche
            wider werden. Als etc. Das wöllen etc. Und biten des <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
            gnedige, <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wider. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>r</ex>ia</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Joh<ex>annis</ex></expan>
<expan>bap<ex>tis</ex><hi rend="sup">te</hi></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
